des: In 2015, Deadeye was founded by two college freshman from Iowa State University. Now you can hear their story or get their recipes right on your couch by talking with Deadeye. Talking with Deadeye creates a whole new experience with food.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
